{"data":[{"date":"07:23 15/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</h2><h2>Ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Jordan. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-tran-mo-man-de-qua-cung-lo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i ch\u1ecbu \u00edt s\u1ee9c \u00e9p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 &quot;d\u1ec5&quot;. Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21. Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t &quot;l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng&quot;, b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ed1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i lo b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian th\u1eed l\u1eeda c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01a1n tru khi ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong kh\u00e2u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00ec &quot;sai s\u00f3t&quot; c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecf qua hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c pha x\u1eed l\u00fd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Olympic-Viet-Nam-thang-Pakistan-Nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m b\u00e0n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u00edt, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ch\u1eaft chiu t\u1eebng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ed1c Tuy\u00ean Quang ph\u1ea3i ra ngh\u1ec9 s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi lo l\u1eafng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Olympic-Viet-Nam-thang-Pakistan-Nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 ASIAD 2018, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/xuan-truong-dinh-chan-thuong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-xau-292-194491.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn tin x\u1ea5u: Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-tran-mo-man-de-qua-cung-lo-292-194489.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n ASIAD 2018: D\u1ec5 qu\u00e1 c\u0169ng... lo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\">HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (KT): M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u1edf ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5505","checkdouble":"194503"},{"date":"07:48 15/08","title":"Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lionel Messi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 Tango \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u \"Leo\" \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ti\u1ebfp theo. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0110T Argentina ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p. HLV Jorge Sampaoli bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n Messi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 im l\u1eb7ng. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Copa America 2016, &quot;Leo&quot; t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T Argentina nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean AFP: &quot;\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Messi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tevez th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, Carlos Tevez nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Messi c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ngay c\u1ea3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 t\u1ed1t hay kh\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh \u1ea5y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Messi. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, Messi v\u1eeba t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fat an \u1ee7i khi c\u00f9ng Barcelona gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla. Chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona v\u1edbi 33 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca-180-194357.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca-184-194199.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cuoc-chien-ronaldo-vs-messi-nong-lan-sang-ca-khoan-du-thuyen-188-193849.html\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Ronaldo vs Messi n\u00f3ng lan sang c\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ... du thuy\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lionel-messi-va-dong-doi-lang-le-ve-hoi-quan-o-barcelona-188-192480.html\">Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-messi-tap-luyen-voi-cho-cung-truoc-mua-giai-moi-188-192416.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5504","checkdouble":"194514"},{"date":"07:07 15/08","title":"Sergio Ramos: \"Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</h2><h2>Kh\u00f4ng Ronaldo, kh\u00f4ng sao c\u1ea3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Atletico t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Real Madrid l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. Cr7 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos c\u00f3 c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thi\u1ebfu Ronaldo, Sergio Ramos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n coi nhau nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;M\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Real Madrid v\u1eabn th\u1ebf th\u00f4i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u0103n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Jurgen Klopp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017-18, Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7y tinh qu\u00e1i khi\u1ebfn Mohamed Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u1ea5t Salah, Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, HLV Jurgen Klopp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng k\u00edch Ramos \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 Sergio Ramos l\u00e0 &quot;t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 t\u00e0n b\u1ea1o&quot;, g\u1ecdi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 &quot;tay \u0111\u00f4 v\u1eadt&quot;. \u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i, Sergio Ramos cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 Salah n\u1eefa, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp thu&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef tay Salah nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y n\u00edu t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u1ed1 l\u00e0m \u0111au b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Klopp mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ec7n minh cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u00f4ng \u1ea5y thua \u1edf chung k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Real Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-muon-no-bom-tan-bld-real-noi-khong-180-194507.html\">HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-148-mu-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-leroy-sane-phien-ban-20-184-194502.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/8: M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Leroy Sane &ldquo;phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nguoi-dai-dien-bao-tin-buon-cho-real-vu-modric-180-194480.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Real v\u1ee5 Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic-180-194470.html\">Real t\u00ednh chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-chot-marcos-alonso-thay-marcelo-180-194461.html\">Real ch\u1ed1t sao Chelsea thay Marcelo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid-180-194418.html\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5503","checkdouble":"194511"},{"date":"08:43 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.</h2><h2>Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Sau nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, Julen Lopetegui chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid. Tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng sau m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 hay ch\u01b0a?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo phat bieu ve Zidane\" title=\"Ronaldo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/cristiano-ronaldo-co-vai-loi-nhan-gui-toi-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ea3 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 HLV Zinedine Zidane \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZinedine Zidane n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay, Cristiano Ronaldo t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, hai c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o c\u00fa hattrick v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Julen Lopetegui l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean \u0111i h\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Zizou, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u00f4ng gi\u00fap &quot;b\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n&quot; gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ba tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid c\u0169ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 l\u1eafng lo ri\u00eang. Ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 l\u00e0 Vinicius Junior ch\u1ec9 \u1edf d\u1ea1ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u &quot;kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng&quot; \u1edf m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eb9 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5p t\u1ec3nh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Marko-Naletilic-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chia tay c\u1ee7a Luka Modric.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Luka Modric v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ra \u0111i&quot;. Marcelo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1ee7 sang Juventus.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Marcelo tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f4i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai: &quot;Gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t cho vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gu\u1ed3ng quay sau nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u1ea8n s\u1ed1 Atletico Madrid<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>So v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, Atletico Madrid r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00edt c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n h\u01a1n. HLV Diego Simeone - ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 cho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Atletico nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua - v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng, ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Antoine Griezmann c\u0169ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi CLB sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Real Madrid vs Atletico\" title=\"Preview Real Madrid vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid - \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAtletico h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao g\u1ed3m Thomas Lemar, Rodri hay Gelson Martin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Diego Simeone \u1edf lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Cagliari - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Khi g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang c\u01a1, Atletico ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (Inter Milan, PSG) v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a (Stuttgart v\u00e0 Arsenal). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean vai th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Diego Simeone \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Trong 5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Real v\u00e0 Atletico m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. Khi Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00f2n Atletico \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, li\u1ec7u c\u00e1n c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nghi\u00eang l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div>* Trong 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1 l\u1ea7n, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.</div>\r\n<div>* Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau 219 l\u1ea7n, Real Madrid th\u1eafng 109 tr\u1eadn, Atletico th\u1eafng 55 l\u1ea7n, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 55 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>* \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean hai HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 Diego Simeone g\u1eb7p nhau.</div>\r\n<div>* T\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Atletico thua 3, h\u00f2a 2 trong s\u1ed1 9 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Real Madrid t\u1ea1i Champions League.</div>\r\n<div>* Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong hai n\u0103m g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (2016 v\u00e0 2017), \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla v\u00e0 Manchester United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>Real Madrid:</strong> Jesus Vallejo, Alvaro Odriozola ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div><strong>Atletico Madrid:</strong> Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8):</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>Real Madrid (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Navas - 2.Carvajal, 5.Varane, 4.Ramos, 12.Marcelo - 14.Casemiro, 8.Kroos - 11.Bale, 22.Isco, 20.Asensio - 9.Benzema</div>\r\n<div><strong>Atletico Madrid (4-4-2): </strong>13.Oblak - 20.Juanfran, 24.Gimenez, 2.Godin, 3.F.Luis - 6.Koke, 5.Partey, 8.Niguez, 11.Lemar - 19.Diego Costa, 7.Griezmann</div>\r\n<div><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Real Madrid 1-2 Atletico Madrid<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Real Madrid vs Atletico\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Real Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-180-194511.html\">Sergio Ramos: Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-muon-no-bom-tan-bld-real-noi-khong-180-194507.html\">HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-148-mu-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-leroy-sane-phien-ban-20-184-194502.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/8: M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Leroy Sane &ldquo;phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nguoi-dai-dien-bao-tin-buon-cho-real-vu-modric-180-194480.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Real v\u1ee5 Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic-180-194470.html\">Real t\u00ednh chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-chot-marcos-alonso-thay-marcelo-180-194461.html\">Real ch\u1ed1t sao Chelsea thay Marcelo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5502","checkdouble":"194518"},{"date":"07:07 15/08","title":"\"M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man United, Paul Scholes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB c\u0169 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng 2 k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1edd Daily Mirror, Scholes th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU. &quot;So v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Liverpool, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecd v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&quot;, Scholes cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a &quot;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho &quot;The Kop&quot; trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. &quot;Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1eef k\u00fd r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&quot;.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Paul-Scholes-Ryan-Giggs-Gary-Neville.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U r\u1ea5t bi quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c cho Man City c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola. &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ea5y MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecd v\u1edbi Man City \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u00ec. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. MU th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng&quot;, Scholes nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u MU nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eabn c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd sai, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda \u0111ua tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y&quot;, Scholes k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ea7y bi quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, MU g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang ba t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53,1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 19,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 1,53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League, MU th\u1eafng Leicester City 2-1 v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Gary Neville, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Scholes v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;th\u1eadt \u0111au l\u00f2ng khi xem MU c\u1ee7a Mourinho thi \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League, MU s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Brighton tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h ng\u00e0y 19/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo TTVN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5501","checkdouble":"194512"},{"date":"07:25 15/08","title":"Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool:\"West Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i M.U hay Man City\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/klopp-liverpool-khong-phai-so-mot-nhung-se-danh-bai-so-mot.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19 nh\u01b0ng HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</h2><h2>Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 The Klopp ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, c\u00e1c m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o LiverpoolWest Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o LiverpoolWest Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/jurgen-klopp-canh-bao-liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf Premier League.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1c quan s\u1edbm b\u1edfi West Ham x\u00e9t cho c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng trung: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0ng West Ham kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man Utd hay Man City&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c qua t\u1eebng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 ai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gary Neville nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Virgil Van Dijk c\u1ee7a Liverpool &quot;gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt&quot;, v\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Jaap Stam. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f9a r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Jurgen Klopp c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng &quot;con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt&quot; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y tr\u00ean France Football, Jurgen Klopp tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ngay: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng, ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd. S\u1ee3 h\u00e3i ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng anh ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c, cao \u0111\u1ebfn 1m91 n\u1eefa. Ngo\u00e0i Van Dijk v\u00e0 Joel Matip, ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf Liverpool hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i cao l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2u&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/jurgen-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-didier-deschamps-184-194483.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;Deschamps khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-nha-cua-liverpool-172-194412.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-mat-an-tuong-cua-naby-keita-172-194366.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Naby Keita?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/naby-keita-ra-mat-an-tuong-cai-gia-cua-su-cho-doi-172-194365.html\">Naby Keita ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: C\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go-172-194348.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-172-194345.html\">HLV Klopp th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung v\u1ec7 Liverpool b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5500","checkdouble":"194513"},{"date":"09:00 15/08","title":"Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/godin-tiet-lo-da-tu-choi-man-united.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Anh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire, Yerry Mina hay Jerome Boateng, Man Utd trong c\u01a1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 khi chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng h\u1ecfi mua Diego Godin, trung v\u1ec7 th\u00e9p c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Godin ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Godin ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/godin-tiet-lo-da-tu-choi-man-united.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Godin ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 to t\u00e1t g\u00ec cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay. Sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u201cch\u1ebft \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ecdc\u201d, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Godin ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Wanda Metropolitano.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00ec l\u00fd do c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfp theo n\u00e0y.\u201d \u2013 Godin mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u khi Atletico \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Real Madrid \u1edf Estonia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Godin v\u1ec1 Old Trafford, HLV Jose Mourinho t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y Man Utd ra l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Atletico tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 7,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro/n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i \u1edf Wanda Metropolitano.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung-184-194143.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung-184-194143.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 10/8: Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5499","checkdouble":"194516"},{"date":"18:57 14/08","title":"Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus khi\u1ebfn Serie A \u201cl\u00ean h\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/matthaus-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-den-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lothar Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa h\u00edch l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Serie A \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ee5p l\u1eb7n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u00f9ng Real Madrid m\u00f9a 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh gia nh\u1eadp Juventus theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real, Ronaldo ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 tr\u1eadn. Anh c\u00f9ng Los Blancos gi\u00e0nh 4 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap Champions League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 5 n\u0103m qua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lothar Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lothar Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/matthaus-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-den-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 Ronaldo, Juventus hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Champions League. 22 n\u0103m qua, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o c\u00fap b\u1ea1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A 7 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMatthaus tin Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u00fa h\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLothar Matthaus, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan (1988 t\u1edbi 1992) d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Cristiano Ronaldo. Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho c\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb\u201d, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Bild. \u201cNh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng xung quanh Ronaldo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Serie A r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o Champions League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Matthaus tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Inter Milan s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Luciano Spalletti \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Juventus c\u1ea1nh tranh Scudetto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cInter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League\u201d, Matthaus n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201ch\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Inter \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018-176-194317.html\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo-176-194058.html\">C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5498","checkdouble":"194487"},{"date":"06:46 15/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Monchi, AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 AS Roma m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 26.65 tri\u1ec7u euro. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Giallorossi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed b\u1ed5 sung 4 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 mang \u0111\u1eadm \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Monchi, b\u1edfi Nzonzi nguy\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u01a1i G\u0110 Monchi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Nzonzi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 ba m\u00f9a thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi AS Roma nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 42.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nzonzi g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 5 trong s\u1ed1 7 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Les Bleus t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Nzonzi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma, Nzonzi cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Roma. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong vi\u1ec7c AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi, G\u0110 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Monchi cho bi\u1ebft: \"Nzonzi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n gi\u1eefa m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nzonzi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh cao h\u01a1n\".<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 AS Roma m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong-180-194430.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/chu-tich-roma-treo-thuong-bang-sieu-xe-lamborghini-188-194092.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roma treo th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng si\u00eau xe Lamborghini</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-193968.html\">Real Madrid 2-1 Roma (KT): Bale t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Los Blancos th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u1edf ICC 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-voi-roma-172-192633.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a-176-192603.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5497","checkdouble":"194508"},{"date":"21:06 14/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3-0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi anh kh\u00f4ng s\u00fat tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang d\u1ed9i ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Paksitan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0\u1eddng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 khao kh\u00e1t ghi b\u00e0n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao. H\u00f4m nay, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 ghi b\u00e0n hay kh\u00f4ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y. Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u1ea5y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ni\u1ec1m tin cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng qu\u00ean \u0111i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal trong 2 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\">HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, \u00f4ng Jose Antonio Noguira, HLV \u0110T Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Olympic Pakistan. L\u1ebd ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5496","checkdouble":"194499"},{"date":"21:25 14/08","title":"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 hai qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/374E6C73000005783745091imagea41_1471435666380.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Pakistan chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 14/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi anh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u00fat tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang d\u1ed9i ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 2 qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda s\u00fat 11m. Song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u1ee7a CLB Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Steaua Bucharest t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng play-off UEFA Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m y chang C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u0169i nh\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 11 m trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i Aguero \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man xanh \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Romania v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Aguero, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 11m trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Oscar. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Brazil khi anh \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 2 qu\u1ea3 11m, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB \u00a0Urawa Reds \u1edf gi\u1ea3i AFC Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 n\u00eau, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Saido Berahino c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty trong tr\u1eadn West Brom g\u1eb7p Watford \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2015/16 hay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Darren Bent b\u1ecf ph\u00ed 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Sunderland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4/2010.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng t\u1edbi 3 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong c\u00f9ng 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Martin Palermo \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia t\u1ea1i Coppa America 1999. T\u1eebng n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t cho huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Batistuta, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martin Palermo v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Olympic Pakistan. L\u1ebd ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5495","checkdouble":"194500"},{"date":"22:40 14/08","title":"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD n\u1ebfu anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n do ch\u00ednh anh v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao HAGL s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, chuy\u00ean gia Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf n\u00f3i tr\u00ean VTC News: \"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00e2m l\u00fd. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi 17, 18 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1ef3, nh\u01b0 Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng m\u00e3i v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nhau. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 - chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, song c\u1ee9 ra s\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u00f4i\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh CLB SLNA H\u1ed3 V\u0103n Chi\u00eam l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u00f4ng \u00fd (HLV Park Hang Seo) cho Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u1eea, th\u00ec c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 tinh t\u1ebf l\u1eafm. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, n\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Thi\u1ebfu g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u201cN\u00f3\u201d - l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng. \u0110\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n h\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng hai l\u1ea7n. Kh\u1ed5 n\u00f3 qu\u00e1, kh\u1ed5 n\u00f3 qu\u00e1\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, BHL Quang Huy l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty v\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede ch\u1ea5m 11 m, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 si\u00eau sao n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng t\u1eebng s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ri\u00eang g\u00ec C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Diego Maradona, Michel Platini \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sau, c\u00f2n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. \u00d4ng Park r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, do \u0111\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, BHL Quang Huy cho bi\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +3, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/8, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nepal l\u00fac 19h00, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan l\u00fac 16h00.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 hai qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16.5pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5494","checkdouble":"194501"},{"date":"23:00 14/08","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/photo1534244610614-1534244610614227491263.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 penalty\u00a0d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 11m n\u1eefa\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat n\u00e0o trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Iraq, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Qatar.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5493","checkdouble":"194504"}]}